data.description: Pack your Bags and bring your Furniture - this home is move in ready and in amazing condition.Appliances are nearly new - in fact the range is brand new - AC recently installed in March of 2018.This four bedroom and two and half bath home in the Ferguson school zone and award winning Clear Creek ISD will bring you years of happiness and warmth. This home includes solid wood shutters which create a rich looking window and a classy look. Surround Sound wired for your music pleasure!Recent upgrades with landscaping too as well as maintenance free siding - never need to paint.This is a one owner home that has been cared for and it shows  - don't miss this one it will go fast.
